9350.title: The French Touch
9350.description: In this comedy, a handsome sheep-shearer finds his magic touch isn't just limited to animals. Shortly after trying his hand as a hairdresser, a client sets him up with his own salon-soon, women are clamoring for an appointment with the man who can change your life with a hairdo!

9470.title: Arizona Seaside
9470.description: A Kazakhstan girl crosses paths with a sweet conman moonlighting as a Robin Hood for stray animals. Both on the run from gangsters they end up at Arizona Seaside, a rundown motel.

9576.title: Two Minute Heist
9576.description: Their plan was flawless... until they put it into action.

21480.title: Kombi Nation
21480.description: Two London-based Australian twenty-somethings, Maggie and Liz, are off on their big adventure - a Kombi van trip around Europe!

131699.title: Bikini Beach Race
131699.description: In this zany comedy, four oddballs and a speedboat pilot team up for a race, and face dangerous curves ahead as the mafia pits the odds against them.

131710.title: Dog Me Potluck
131710.description: Hilarious comedy about a couple having marital problems who decide to have a potluck dinner with some of their friends to shake up their marriage

258335.title: Film Crew: Wild Women of Wongo
258335.description: The beautiful women of the lush, tropical island of Wongo are led to believe the only men who exist are the horribly ugly, ape-like creatures that live on the other side of the island.

264333.title: Young and Handsome: A Night with Jeff Garlin
264333.description: Jeff Garlin, known by many for his role as Jeff Greene on Curb Your Enthusiasm, returns to his hometown and his comedy roots for his first hour-long special.

286051.title: He's Way More Famous Than You
286051.description: When indie starlet Halley Feiffer loses her boyfriend, her agent and her career in one fell swoop, she realizes that something has to change...she has to become WAY MORE FAMOUS!

290645.title: A Free Bird
290645.description: Down-on-his-luck, TJ opts in when his buddies hatch a plan to rob the steakhouse that just fired him for a helping of free meat. What could go wrong?

318226.title: The Colour of Funny
318226.description: Multicultural stand-up performances from the Just For Laughs festival. Featuring Godfrey & more.

321309.title: Republic Of Pete
321309.description: Pete and his idiot friends receive $80 million from his grandfather trying to protect himself in a lawsuit. They decide to purchase an island with strippers and are happy until evil grandfather wants his money back.

327640.title: Are You Joking?
327640.description: Twenty-something New Yorker Barb Schwartz somehow ended up in a life that kinda... sucks. When she is reunited with her childhood BFF, ballet dancer Billy, she is inspired to turn her life around by revisiting her first love: comedy.

327702.title: Indian Comedy Tour
327702.description: A hilarious night of comedy with five of the funniest Indian stand-up comedians! Blowing aside political correctness, these talented Indian comics break down stereotypes as they cover politics, racism, dating, childhood and pop-culture.

327725.title: Sam Kinison: Live in Vegas
327725.description: Sam Kinison gives a completely raw and uncensored performance at the very height of his career. Filled with scorching comedy, hot women and sizzling rock 'n roll, this show encapsulates the energy and relentless brand of comedy that was unique to Kinison.

330134.title: Meeting Spencer
330134.description: After a series of Hollywood flops, famed director Harris Chappell returns to New York to relaunch his Broadway career. But Chappell's triumphant comeback begins to spiral out of control into a wild night of comic misadventure after meeting struggling actor Spencer and his old flame Didi.

341842.title: Clunkers
341842.description: When an injury crushes his dreams of going pro, an aspiring baseball player moves back home and joins a team of questionable car salesmen.

363140.title: C Street
363140.description: C STREET is about an intern who pimps out his apartment to sex-starved politicians, until he finds the girl of his dreams naked in his bed.

367623.title: 18 Year Old Virgin
367623.description: A teenager is determined to lose her virginity before she graduates so she can have sex with her crush, who refuses to sleep with virgins.

367674.title: Celebrity Sex Tape
367674.description: After secretly recording a has-been celebrity having sex, several college nerds have the attention of every B-list celebrity in Hollywood.

369845.title: Dangerous Curves
369845.description: In this youth-oriented comedy Chuck and Wally are friends in their senior year of college with graduation fast approaching. A wealthy industrialist offers them jobs after graduation if they'll do him a favor and deliver a car to his daughter in Lake Tahoe. The car, a red Porsche, gets stolen for use as the prize in a beauty pageant. The lads wind up in San Diego attempting to recover the car and preserve their future careers.

376072.title: My Five Wives
376072.description: When Monte Peterson purchases land in Utah, he discovers it comes with five new wives. As he tries to keep up, gangsters plot to take it all away.

376080.title: The Newest Pledge
376080.description: A hard-partying fraternity decides to pledge a baby that they find on their doorstep the morning after their most decadent party of the semester. Through the hilarious hurdles that the Omegas endure raising this baby, their rival fraternity, Phi Tau, learns of their pledge plan. In order for Phi Tau to stay as the number one fraternity on campus, they'll do whatever they can to ruin this newest pledge's chances of a frat life.

376164.title: Hittin' It!
376164.description: Things get out of hand for a pair of college roommates throwing a party at an uncle’s beach house once an unhinged cousin crashes the bash.

386213.title: Hollywood Road Trip
386213.description: Chaz, a vintage magazine collector, decides to go on a road trip with his friends to Hollywood after discovering his landlord's plot to find and hurt its long time founder and CEO. With everything at stake, he is forced to choose between his magazine collection, his best friends, his dream girl or saving an innocent man's life.

394219.title: The Kebab Incident
394219.description: Johann Stanzerl feels hemmed in. Every other business in his Viennese neighbourhood is owned by a Turk. Only his beloved Cafe Prinz Eugen is still offering any resistance, with its regular, upstanding, Austrian clientele. To Johann's surprise, he and his wife were not the only ones extending their cafe. Mustafa, the Turkish businessman from next door also expanded his new restaurant. The Count had obviously sold the same premises twice. Could this possibly get worse for Johann? The enemies both live in and own his building. The Turkish neighbour must go, no matter the cost.

401154.title: Alonzo Bodden: Tall, Dark and Funny
401154.description: Alonzo hilariously touches upon every subject from tsunamis to terrorists, Democrats to desperate housewives, marriage to midgets, and more,

401165.title: Kims of Comedy
401165.description: The Original Kims break new ground with an uncompromising look at Asian culture and some hilarious ethnic hang-ups. Featured are 4 of the top Asian comedians on stage today: Bobby Lee, Kevin Shea, Steve Byrne, and Dr. Ken Jeong.

439009.title: Rent a Car
439009.description: The hilarious story of a rental car business owner named 'D-Stacks' and his dedicated, but sometimes demented, employees.

439015.title: A Night in Compton
439015.description: A young man home from college on Christmas break has intimate plans with his new love interest, but a night of interruptions makes for a zany time.

440277.title: The Awkward Comedy Show
440277.description: An African-American showcase featuring comedians riffing on all things nerdy and hilarious, from computer programming to Shakespearean drama.

445019.title: Bikini Model Academy
445019.description: When broke beach buddies get dumped by their girlfriends, an uncle helps them start a bikini modeling academy, but an old rival starts his own school.

449509.title: Ernest's Greatest Hits (Vol. 1)
449509.description: Before he went to camp, before he saved Christmas, or was scared stupid in the movies, comedy’s Ernest hosted the classic commercials collected here.

452585.title: The Nasty Show
452585.description: Prepare yourself for a night of comedy featuring some of comedy’s filthiest minds, and see for yourself why this is one of JFL’s most popular shows.

453775.title: Tim & Eric's Billion Dollar Movie
453775.description: After wasting their movie's billion-dollar budget, Tim and Eric take a job rehabilitating a bankrupt mall full of eccentric characters.

460301.title: Believe
460301.description: A comedy set within the world of multi-level marketing.

461548.title: Ham and Cheese
461548.description: Two friends try to make it through the highs and lows of showbiz as actors, armed with persistence but unfortunately lacking any discernible talent.

463669.title: Hey Mr. Postman
463669.description: When he loses his job, Brian gets a hook up at the neighborhood post office where he learns just how challenging being the local mailman can be.

466927.title: State Park
466927.description: Carefree teenagers get wild in the wilderness on the last week of summer, while a businessman's plans for dumping toxic waste go gloriously awry.

467487.title: Alex Thomas
467487.description: Comedian Alex Thomas doesn't pull any punches in this no-holds-barred comedy special that mixes old school style with new school flavor.

467986.title: The Pickle Recipe
467986.description: A party MC, who is strapped for cash, gets corrupted into stealing the prized dill pickle recipe his grandma swore she would to take to her grave.

468597.title: The Hustle
468597.description: When two exterminators trying to make extra cash end up in major debt to a crime boss, being mistaken for Baptist ministers is their saving grace.

468604.title: The Foursome
468604.description: Friends reunite on a golf course at their 20th college reunion, encountering sand traps and old grudges, and taking aim at the holes in their lives.

468754.title: Fell, Jumped or Pushed
468754.description: An amateur filmmaker investigates the bizarre disappearance of his grandfather decades before in this outrageously entertaining mockumentary.

470576.title: Squatters
470576.description: Two struggling entertainers find themselves on the street and decide to squat in the home of a vacationing family while they get their lives together.

472146.title: Frostbite!
472146.description: A law associate on a hometown business trip has to help his buddies save their ski waxing business while evading shady businessmen and a Sasquatch.

476919.title: DaGram
476919.description: A relatable urban comedy about the unintentional consequences that happen to the most well-intentioned people when they try to front on social media.

485825.title: Viral Viral
485825.description: Three online video creators are trying in vain to create a viral video. A darkly comedic tale of the crackpot underbelly of public media where nothing is off-limits in the quest for hits.

485939.title: More Money, More Family
485939.description: When a family rivalry goes too far, two cousins buy a lottery ticket to lure the family back together, but things go horribly wrong.

486057.title: Chee and T
486057.description: Chee and T are underachieving debt collectors stuck in Silicon Valley, who spend their days collecting rent and chain smoking. When their wealthy Uncle Rob asks them to do a seemingly small job, the task proves to be anything but simple.

489063.title: Destination: Dewsbury
489063.description: Four mid-life blokes from the United Kingdom go on a wild road trip across England to see a dying schoolmate, regressing to their rowdy and rude ways.

490121.title: Colin & Brad
490121.description: Colin Mochrie and Brad Sherwood, stars of the Emmyr-winning Whose Line Is It Anyway?, have finally recorded their hilarious live stage show!! These masters of improv comedy have performed their outrageous, one-of-a-kind show to sold out audiences all over the country. Colin and Brad's TWO MAN GROUP is a riotously funny, interactive, and completely improvised tour de force. Using nothing but their lightning fast wits and some audience volunteers, Colin and Brad create pandemonium on the spot in one of the funniest live shows you will ever see.

490955.title: My Best Friend's Famous
490955.description: An insecure New Yorker moves to Los Angeles and grapples with jealousy when his less-talented best friend becomes a star on a hit television show.

491932.title: Lost & Found in Armenia
491932.description: Mistaken identity takes a hilarious turn when a U.S. senator’s son crash lands in an Armenian village and is accused of being a Turkish spy.

492253.title: Sharp as Marbles
492253.description: Three roommates work together at a video store and they all lean on each other for support, but not one of them has an intelligent thought to share.

492255.title: Man Overboard
492255.description: With his boat dealership financially underwater, a desperate businessman makes the mistake of hiring a fast-talking, unscrupulous salesman.

494694.title: Red Skelton: Bloopers, Blunders & Ad-Libs
494694.description: Comedy legend Red Skelton was at his best when he strayed from the script, and these classic bloopers and ad-libs will prove his comedy is timeless.

495831.title: RiffTrax Live: Night of the Shorts - A Good Day to Riff Hard - SF Sketchfest 2015
495831.description: The insanely quick-witted, hilarious crew returns to riff on more shorts, this time with the mundane and bizarre favorite, Setting Up a Room.

495833.title: RiffTrax Live: Summer Shorts Beach Party
495833.description: When the sun’s out, you know it’s time for the RiffTrax crew to give their amusing commentary on beloved and inexplicable educational shorts.

497890.title: Bald
497890.description: An undersexed college student who’s going bald raises money for a hair transplant by starting a softcore porn site on campus.

498584.title: Young Nurses in Love
498584.description: A Russian mole poses as an American nurse to steal the DNA of world leaders from a sperm bank, but she keeps getting thrown off by a handsome doctor.

498646.title: Hollywood Palms
498646.description: Hilarious slice of life about the exploits of various residents living in a Hollywood apartment complex and dealing with daily life in Los Angeles.

501276.title: RiffTrax: Santa and the Ice Cream Bunny
501276.description: Few movies have made quite an impression on the riff crew as this classic, which features gorilla suits, santa costumes, and a nonsensical plot.

501292.title: RiffTrax Live: Christmas Shortstravaganza
501292.description: Join your favorite funny fellows, plus musical guest “Weird Al” Yankovic, for a night of ice-skating reindeer, smoking santas, and hilarious riffs.

504739.title: Firehouse
504739.description: Three sexy women fresh out of fire school enlist in an all-male fire station, when an arsonist sets fires to old buildings in a run-down neighborhood.

508022.title: Angry White Man
508022.description: When a disaster ruins his wedding, a southern-fried redneck with nothing to lose takes his buddy on a crazy road trip in hopes of meeting his idol.

509107.title: Kickin' It Old Skool
509107.description: A young breakdancer wakes up from a 20-year coma and tries to revive his team’s career with the help of his girlfriend and his parents.

509108.title: Jamie Kennedy: Unwashed
509108.description: TV and film star Jamie Kennedy (Scream) performs his first stand-up concert special, filmed before a sold-out audience at the San Jose Theater.

513107.title: KevCoin: The Movie
513107.description: An eager entrepreneur seeks backers to fund his dream of creating a cryptocurrency token, dubbed KevCoin, valued at one trillion dollars.

513969.title: Captain Hagen's Bed & Breakfast
513969.description: Four couples spend a wild weekend in the Hamptons at an unusual bed and breakfast, run by a quirky German boat captain and his eccentric family.

517454.title: Erik Myers: Dopeless Romantic
517454.description: The energetic comic performs in Florida’s historic Polk Theatre before a sold-out crowd, as he discusses his everyday conundrums.

519962.title: Appiness
519962.description: After losing his job, Eric’s chance meeting with an old high school buddy leads to a start-up adventure to develop the next great app.

520466.title: Letters From a Nut
520466.description: Produced by Jerry Seinfeld, a writer’s deliberately off-the-wall prank letters, and the replies he gets back, are hilariously brought to the screen.

522161.title: Kevin Hart - Live Comedy From the Laff House
522161.description: Superstar Kevin Hart performs hilarious live stand-up at the Laff House in Philadelphia, filmed before he was a worldwide star.

525186.title: Bringing Up Bobby
525186.description: The reading of their late parents’ will brings orphaned siblings together and puts the focus on a teenage son’s acceptance of Jesus and himself.

526711.title: RiffTrax: Night of the Shorts: SF Sketchfest 2013
526711.description: The RiffTrax crew hosts an evening of seven terrible shorts, hilarious guest stars, and witty commentary. Who could ask for anything more?

529001.title: Admins
529001.description: A day in the lives of two computer system admins follows them as they annoy users, discuss office politics, and watch gophers at the coffee shop.

529004.title: Roscoe's House of Chicken and Waffles
529004.description: A numbers runner in a mess with the mob leaps from the frying pan into the fire, as he schemes to profit by bringing fame and fortune to an LA eatery.

530295.title: Switchin' the Script
530295.description: During a weekend retreat, an unlucky-in-love woman’s best friends convince her to "switch the script" and take control of her search for “Mr. Right.”

533599.title: Round Trip to Heaven
533599.description: When two awkward guys borrow a Rolls-Royce to impress a model, they inadvertently become a part of a dangerous robbery and epic chase.

534930.title: The Luau
534930.description: Against his father’s wishes, a young man with gambling debts tries to get paid and lei’d by throwing a big luau, which quickly spirals out of control.

543338.title: Super Sucker
543338.description: When two competing door-to-door vacuum cleaner distributors race to see who can sell the most in 30 days, things quickly get out of hand.

547550.title: Gary Owen: Breakin' Out the Park
547550.description: In this brutally honest stand-up performance, comedian Gary Owen confesses his hilarious history of growing up in and around trailer parks.

547561.title: Debra DiGiovanni: Single, Awkward, Female
547561.description: The Canadian comedian known for her work as a finalist on Last Comic Standing discusses her takes on dating, dieting, and modern romance.

547572.title: 37-Teen
547572.description: Billionaire Adam Pi uses his wealth to relive his senior year of high school, only this time he’s determined to have a better experience.

551876.title: Thou Shalt Laugh 5: Chonda Pierce
551876.description: "The Queen of Clean," humorist Chondra Pierce, shares stories about her southern upbringing and  headlines a lineup of Christian stand-up comics.

551878.title: Thou Shalt Laugh, the Deuce: Tim Conway
551878.description: Funnyman Tim Conway presents a roster of America’s zaniest Christian comedians, including SNL alum, Victoria Jackson and other clean cut-ups.

551973.title: Thou Shalt Laugh: Patricia Heaton
551973.description: Flat-out fun for the whole family awaits, as Emmy-winner Patricia Heaton hosts a lineup featuring seven of the funniest Christian comics around.

552275.title: Reality Queen
552275.description: After a drunken fall lands a beautiful young heiress and reality TV star in the hospital, she struggles to claw her way back to her unearned fame.

552960.title: Goin' All the Way
552960.description: A teenager whose girlfriend won't go all the way attempts to lose his virginity with the help of his wiseguy best friend.

557266.title: The Misery Brothers
557266.description: When two misfits set out on a journey to correct their cursed family's misfortunes, they encounter wacky surprises at every turn.

557669.title: #DigitalLivesMatter
557669.description: Hijinks ensue, when a disgruntled fan of a social media superstar hacks into his Instagram account and removes the star's millions of followers.

558744.title: Bros. on the Rocks
558744.description: The bromance rules as two pals go for a night on the town in Waterloo, Iowa and get shamed by a public prank, only to seek revenge in another town.

560229.title: Chonda Pierce: Be Afraid... Be Very Afraid
560229.description: The funny lady looks fear in the eye and laughs, sharing her secret weapons: comedy sketches, faux commercials, stories, and heartfelt songs

560233.title: Chonda Pierce: Stayin' Alive...Laughing
560233.description: The comic dances her way through empty nesting, group therapy, two-steppin' and twelve-stepping, a cameo by Bill Gaither, and a song from Russ Taff.

560495.title: Worst Roommate Ever
560495.description: A med student and his best friend must learn to live together while dealing with an eccentric landlord, high school crushes and nagging parents.

560628.title: I Got Five on It 3
560628.description: With Barney away at seminary school, his friends Oscar and Jimmy are stuck dealing with old foes who have just been released from prison.

560646.title: I Got Five on It
560646.description: All Jimmy and his pals want is to be invited to an epic party. Instead, they find themselves thrown into a wacky, hilarious crosstown adventure.

561319.title: The Big Black Comedy Show (Vol. 1)
561319.description: Oscar-winning actress/ hilarious stand up Mo'Nique co-hosts this all-star comedy show featuring some of the best comics in the business.

561320.title: The Big Black Comedy Show (Vol. 2)
561320.description: Award-winning comedian/actress Mo'Nique returns as the co-host of this hilarious special, which includes a killer lineup of comics.

561321.title: The Big Black Comedy Show (Vol. 4)
561321.description: Ralphie May hosts this laugh-a-minute comedy special, which includes hilarious comics like Jay Phillips, Tommy Chunn, Alex Thomas, and more.

561322.title: The Big Black Comedy Show (Vol. 3)
561322.description: The always hilarious Michael Colyar and DeRay Davis host this amazing lineup of comedic talent, including Retha Jones, and Lil Rel Howery.

562051.title: Thou Shalt Laugh 3: Sinbad
562051.description: Comedy superstar Sinbad and his roster of top Christian humorists provide funny, family-friendly entertainment, in this episode of the series.

562959.title: Death & Taxes: The Second Coming of Harold Hoptuit
562959.description: On the day his former wife gets engaged, a man mysteriously rises from the dead, hoping for a second chance to be a better husband and father.

563509.title: Laugh Til It Hurtz
563509.description: Hosted by comedy sensation Ax’nt, this hilarious special features some of the funniest clean comedians in the entertainment industry.

563925.title: Crush(ed)
563925.description: A fluffy, hapless man with no money, a cop on his back, and a room in his mother’s house is about to defy the odds all the way to the wedding altar.

564437.title: Joe Pasquale: Bubble & Squeak
564437.description: Creative comedian Pasquale generates laughter from his unusual performances which include hilarious songs, sketches, and other gags.

564745.title: Wally Got Wasted
564745.description: A fun evening in Los Angeles turns into a hilarious nightmare when three friends accidentally kill a jerk, then are forced to pretend he’s alive.

565668.title: Unapologetical
565668.description: Comedian Brad Stine brings his comedy to the stage for this stand-up special riffing on touching strangers, the magical powers of women and more.

565889.title: Tony Roberts: I'm Different
565889.description: In a stand-up performance for the ages, the gifted comic, TV star, and BET award winner riffs on Eddie Murphy, parenting, sex, and life's absurdities.

566333.title: You Lucky People
566333.description: A charming comedy about a group of British privates at a military reserve whose two-week training is at direct odds with their hapless hijinks.

566343.title: Senior Week
566343.description: An overnight road trip to Florida goes left for a car full of teenage guys after two jealous girlfriends and an unhinged teacher enter the picture.

566368.title: Fun at St Fanny's
566368.description: A 25-year-old is prevented from graduating, so his school headmaster can live off and bet with the money that the student’s uncle left in his will.

568056.title: Black Magic for White Boys
568056.description: To keep his cash-strapped business from shuttering, a desperate theater owner cracks a book of magic spells and learns he can make people disappear.

569456.title: Meet Wally Sparks
569456.description: A brash TV host will stop at nothing to get his ratings boost, including going to the governor's mansion to break a scandalous story.

570420.title: The Bachelor Party 2: It's a Wonderful Lifestyle (The Rise of Showstopper)
570420.description: This hilarious spoof of spy films takes to the skies with a cocky bachelor and the galaxy’s most beautiful blonde out to save the world from darkness.

571533.title: Leon the Pig Farmer
571533.description: A sensitive London man learns that his birth was the result of artificial insemination, and that his biological father is someone he'd never expect.

573113.title: Rock, Paper, Scissors: The Way of the Tosser
573113.description: The crown at the 2006 Rock Paper Scissors World Championship isn’t going to win itself so Gary and friends get their hand Zen on to reign supreme.

575224.title: Donzilla the Comedy Monster
575224.description: The uncensored and adult observations from comedian Donzilla are back in this proudly tasteless stand-up set that is not for the weak of heart!

577680.title: How to Murder Your Wife
577680.description: A rich bachelor finds his swinging lifestyle ruined when he awakens one morning having married the gorgeous lady who popped out of a cake.

579183.title: The Blind Date
579183.description: A comedian has a blind date with a woman he’s never seen, and she doesn’t know that their first date will be onstage in front of a live audience.

579375.title: Happy's
579375.description: Slice-of-life comedy about a man who moves to Iowa for a scholarship that falls apart, only to become a liquor store clerk with a quirky legal mentor.

579568.title: Women vs. Men
579568.description: After two middle-aged married men are caught at a scandalous strip club by their wives, everyone realizes their own fears about aging and sex.

581075.title: The Grail
581075.description: As Johnny is about to move out of his house with a pair of roommates who refuse to grow up, the men live up their last night as an immature trio.

581669.title: Firesign Theatre's Hot Shorts
581669.description: The comedy quartet reimagines 1940’s Saturday afternoon serials by imbuing them with their own satirical dialog, music, and sound effects.

585708.title: Go for Broke 2
585708.description: Desperate for ransom money when their best friend is kidnapped, John and Darnell dress in drag to steal a $20 million diamond from an African prince.

586542.title: Claudia Oshry: Disgraced Queen
586542.description: As Instagram’s reigning disgraced queen, the comic takes on pop culture and all that is wrong with it, in an outrageous new stand-up comedy special.

587047.title: Grass
587047.description: A straight-laced woman asks her friend for help delivering a backpack full of weed for her drug-dealer fiancé, but things quickly get out of hand.

588409.title: Selling Stupid
588409.description: A pair of female advertising executives are pitted against two male colleagues by their sexist boss to create a campaign for a new video game.

589844.title: Eddie Pence: The (Un)Special Comedy Special
589844.description: The comic and podcaster performs before his hometown of Washington D.C. to talk about relationship issues, Star Wars lines, and so much more.

589846.title: Tom Wilson: Bigger Than You
589846.description: Best known for his role as Biff Tannen in the Back to the Future series, comic Tom Wilson tells some hilarious stories and plays a little guitar.

589852.title: The Social Ones
589852.description: When five social media influencers learn that they’ll grace the cover of a magazine, they start to experience anxiety about their impending success.

589862.title: Hannibal Thompson: Out of Control
589862.description: Performing before a Sacramento crowd, the honest comic delivers gut-busting bits of truth on family, the holidays, and the cost of living.

589866.title: Michael Loftus: You've Changed
589866.description: In his first ever one hour special, the comedian discusses all that is great, challenging, and everything in between on the subject of marriage.

591197.title: The Many Sides of Don Rickles
591197.description: Classic television and insult comic extraordinaire Don Comics come together in his first prime time network special that aired on ABC in 1970.

592401.title: Boys vs. Girls
592401.description: When a 90’s camp director makes his summer program co-ed, the boys and the girls get into an epic battle of the sexes to prove who’s the best.

592419.title: Mags and Julie Go on a Road Trip
592419.description: To escape everyday work challenges, two best friends head out for a weekend cabin adventure, which is not quite what they imagined.

594912.title: Don Rickles: Alive and Kicking
594912.description: This special, introduced by Johnny Carson and featuring famous comics, showcases the master of insults, spouting hilarious put-downs and one-liners.

595065.title: Mr. Warmth
595065.description: A television comedy/variety special hosted by comedian Don Rickles. Highlights include: a comedy sketch between Rickles and John Wayne; a spoof on situation comedy shows featuring Rickles in drag; several brief cameos from Carroll O'Connor

595860.title: Slapjack
595860.description: A not-so-average guy gets kicked out of the house, enrolled in a strange university, and ordered to share a small dorm room with a quirky girl, all while balancing a self-help class and aspirations of being a singing star.

595869.title: The Naked Truth
595869.description: Two friends, both named Frank, accidentally obtain a suitcase at the airport. It contains incriminating evidence against a mafia boss, who sends his Terminator-like lackie to find them. The Franks hide by impersonating make-up women for a beauty pageant. While in drag, the mafioso falls in love with one of the Franks.

598873.title: Sofa King
598873.description: A charming indie comedy proving sometimes to move forward, you have to sit still.

602986.title: Grand Opening
602986.description: Winning the lottery means Pablo can fulfill his dream of owning a successful grocery store if not for the myriad disasters that unfold in the process.

603040.title: Good Grief: A Comedy About Loss and Being Bad at It
